name: Onus EP
description:
Belle Haven's 2012 EP titled "Onus"!

The single "Sister-In-Law" is available for free streaming at http://listn.to/BelleHaven

Included inside is a 5 track CD tracked, produced and mastered by Callan Orr of Dream On, Dreamer at Avalanche Studios. Also included is an 8 page booklet containing lyrics and artwork by Ashlee Jayde.

Additional vocals on "Sister-In-Law" provided by Miles Philipp of Glorified! and Bianca Becker.

Track Listing:
1. Ideal Victims
2. A Cancer Upon My Body
3. Sister-In-Law
4. For What Is Now Lost
5. The Bunker

Expect at least 3-5 days for delivery in Australia and at least 7-10 days for International delivery.

If there are any issues with your order, please contact us at bellehavenband@hotmail.com.
